### **Combining the data.frame**

Monthly Sales


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
spark <- report %>%
  group_by(Product) %>%
  summarize('Monthly Sales' = list(Sales), 
            .groups = "drop")
```
:::


Sales statistics


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
sales <- report %>% 
  group_by(Product) %>% 
  summarise("Min" = min(Sales, na.rm = T),
            "Max" = max(Sales, na.rm = T),
            "Average" = mean(Sales, na.rm = T)
            )
```
:::


Combine all


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
sales_data = left_join(sales, spark)
```
:::


